or born 1942)|John McCarthy]]||2001||2004||<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.foreignminister.gov.au/releases/2001/fa033_01.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212022723/http://www.foreignminister.gov.au/releases/2001/fa033_01.html|archivedate=12 February 2014|url-status=live|first=Alexander|last=Downer|date=19 March 2001|author-link=Alexander Downer|publisher=Australian Government| title=Diplomatic Appointment: Ambassador to Japan }}</ref>\n|-\n||[[Murray McLean (ambassador)|Murray McLean]]||2004||2011||<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.foreignminister.gov.au/releases/2004/fa085_04.html|title=Diplomatic Appointment: Ambassador to Japan|date=17 June 2004|first=Alexander|last=Downer|author-link=Alexander Downer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212013521/http://www.foreignminister.gov.au/releases/2004/fa085_04.html|archivedate=12 February 2014|url-status=dead|publisher=Australian Government|access-date=9 February 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n||[[Bruce Miller (diplomat)|Bruce Miller]]||August 2011||December 2016||<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://foreignminister.gov.au/releases/Pages/2011/kr_mr_110407.aspx?ministerid=2 |title=Diplomatic appointment: Ambassador to Japan |date=7 April 2011 |first=Kevin |last=Rudd |author-link=Kevin Rudd |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714120316/http://foreignminister.gov.au/releases/Pages/2011/kr_mr_110407.aspx?ministerid=2 |archivedate=14 July 2014 |publisher=Australian Government }}</ref><ref>{{citation|url=http://dfat.gov.au/about-us/our-people/homs/Pages/ambassador-to-japan.aspx|title=Ambassador to Japan: Mr Bruce Miller|archivedate=14 August 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814055100/http://dfat.gov.au/about-us/our-people/homs/Pages/ambassador-to-japan.aspx|publisher=Australian Government|author=Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Diplomatic appointment: Ambassador to Japan |url=http://foreignminister.gov.au/releases/Pages/20